desc_long								关于这款游戏							A violent murder has awoken a small town with a troubled past. A town where evil was part of their history, fear was in their daily lives. They thought that chapter was over with. But has it returned? Features:•	Investigate a string of murders.•	Solve puzzles crafted to stop you.•	Meet townsfolk and hear their stories.•	Search for relevant clues and use them to catch a killer.						
